##
## Arch Linux repository mirrorlist
## Managed in fork: default/pacman/mirrorlist-stable
##
## Pointing at vanilla Arch CDN mirrors instead of stable-mirror.omarchy.org
## (which lags upstream Arch by 1-2 weeks).
##
## Both entries below are CDN-backed and geo-distributed, so they stay fast
## regardless of physical location. Cloudflare is primary; the official Arch
## redirector is the fallback.
##

## Worldwide CDN
Server = https://cloudflaremirrors.com/archlinux/$repo/os/$arch

## Official Arch mirror redirector (geo-routes to nearest tier-1)
Server = https://geo.mirror.pkgbuild.com/$repo/os/$arch
